{"tid":1647113,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底應該點做？","createTime":"2019-10-11T15:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T16:36:12.000Z","uid":154063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc1fea488ffc121082ae9f784e1678ad30ee56b","tid":1647113,"uid":154063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"話說之前玩活動識咗個男仔<br />\n有次outing 同佢同team<br />\n咁佢有好多主動嘅行為 例如請飲野 主動同我坐<br />\n成日outing都同佢一齊<br />\n我feel到有啲野嘅<br />\n佢又主動加ig<br />\n之後我都有同佢講下野 但一句起 兩句止<br />\n佢又唔喺成日覆<br />\n宜家都唔肯定佢喺唔喺真喺對我有野<br />\n聽人講男仔有feel嘅應該會主動去馬<br />\n到底即喺點啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我做主動都無問題 但好難突然間冇咩交流而有下一步<br />\n想請教點樣同佢開始個對話 令我地可以日日有計傾咁<br />\n<br />\n利申A0 同佢同校唔同科<br />\n我嘅幸福靠大家啦<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><br />\n雖然國難當前 兒女私情應該放低<br />\n但真喺好辛苦 好想有個人可以陪下我<br />\n希望大家體諒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span>"},{"pid":"5714b2131388199eb21090a428af005487c30b4e","tid":1647113,"uid":2676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:20:36.000Z","msg":"善用不推文"},{"pid":"5a9b6198463456ba882fd4df4f57164cc2d4c10e","tid":1647113,"uid":8730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:21:01.000Z","msg":"[極緊急］星期日急需一場真正嘅十八區再開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日五區打遊擊 星期一三罷</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"192773eec3ab1c0ec95e5eeac853f80951f6a1b8","tid":1647113,"uid":256640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bc1fea488ffc121082ae9f784e1678ad30ee56b","tid":1647113,"uid":154063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"repl